    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《宇宙光波》重新定义了方块破坏这款经典街机游戏。除了方块和掉落宝物等玩家熟悉的游戏元素外，它也融合了许多酷炫的新功能，比如：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/0f41c8c663118f20b086030fd44e6d01.poster.avif?t=1753783483\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/0f41c8c663118f20b086030fd44e6d01.webm?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/0f41c8c663118f20b086030fd44e6d01.mp4?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>力波发射塔</strong> - 用塔控制球的方向，增强球的力量，冲破方块，激活关卡上不同物体的反应。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/cbd8f6d9499109402a88ea93822833ef.poster.avif?t=1753783483\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/cbd8f6d9499109402a88ea93822833ef.webm?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/cbd8f6d9499109402a88ea93822833ef.mp4?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bosses大决战</strong> - 不仅要破坏方块，还要与 Boss 巅峰对决！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/f1fdbebacddb9ee9bc26f1b087deff08.poster.avif?t=1753783483\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/f1fdbebacddb9ee9bc26f1b087deff08.webm?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/f1fdbebacddb9ee9bc26f1b087deff08.mp4?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奖励关卡</strong> - 完成奖励关卡，获得更多积分！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>破坏方块</strong> - 还有什么比破坏方块更好玩呢？击打或射击方块，都会碎成碎片！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/fe6a23d1c6da4ce302e6396dbd3c609a.avif?t=1753783483\" width=612 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态相机</strong> - 既然玩法这么多，为什么总从同一个角度玩 ，同一关卡中也可以切换视角。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间操纵</strong> - 和塔巧妙配合，会产生超棒的连击效果。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同关卡的物体</strong> - 只有方块也许会无聊，还有更多乐趣等你发现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超酷的角色</strong> - 你可以自主选择角色，每个角色都有专属的特殊攻击，沿途中也会遇到新朋友 。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超棒的音乐</strong> - 美妙配乐由歌手 Module亲自制作！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/954440b259e3a4e864b5a5073ada927e.poster.avif?t=1753783483\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/954440b259e3a4e864b5a5073ada927e.webm?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292540/extras/954440b259e3a4e864b5a5073ada927e.mp4?t=1753783483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁完整版，探索更多精彩：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进度系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新终极Boss 和敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更多新角色和关卡</strong></p>",
